[06:41.81]First Citizen	For mine own part,
[06:43.21]	When I said, banish him, I said 'twas pity.
[06:45.89]Second Citizen	And so did I.
[06:47.00]Third Citizen	And so did I; and, to say the truth, so did very
[06:50.03]	many of us: that we did, we did for the best; and
[06:53.12]	though we willingly consented to his banishment, yet
